{"tid":2283003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人粵語句子中英夾雜的背後心理戰術","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T20:03:15.000Z","uid":47901,"like":19,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"56711fbc8f31951ecbb32b67ab4f671bfa689b66","tid":2283003,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"首先，講成句英文，一串長句子的危險在於，出錯機會好大，一俾人捉錯就好撚麻煩，你知香港人，特別係八婆之間實會互相咬閪住對方的錯誤唔放<br />\n<br />\n粵語句子中間&ldquo;撻&rdquo;一個英文字或者phrase, 其背後原因是應用心理戰術，因為可以先製造&ldquo;大&rdquo;到對方的機會<br />\n<br />\n就好似在玩卡Game的情況，雖然唔確定對方會點反制，但因應對手的習性同慣用策略，同佢所用的卡組（deck) , 同埋當下的成個牌局，先出某張可以令對手之後會麻撚煩的牌，即係先發制人，去製造一個戰略高地，使對手往後的行動同士氣可預先被自己大大限制住<br />\n<br />\n如果對方唔識自己句中某隻英文字或者phrase，你就可以先取得戰術同士氣上的優勢，而如果對方膽敢問：&ldquo;下？果隻英文字係咩意思呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;，即係自投羅網等俾人玩到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，就算句子中只夾雜英語單詞或者簡短的phrase, 都有機會產生極為危險的用錯的情況，為免出洋相同令自己被對方狙擊而無地自容，一般香港人會大量在粵語句子中運用自己非常熟悉慣用，同自己滿有信心可以把握正確用法的英文字詞或phrase, 其作用在於可以大量運用英文而又可以盡量減低出錯機會<br />\n<br />\n以上係香港人之間，尤其是八婆之間，長年心戰經驗而自然漸漸形成的society spontaneous gradual optimization of conventional interpersonal psychological warfare tactics and strategies."},{"pid":"87e45a7571541ccf1e0e23548fddb2d2710901fa","tid":2283003,"uid":47901,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"所以，八婆世界常有粵語句子中夾雜大量根本完全就冇需要用英文而可以直接用粵語的字或phrase, 例如，頭髮要用hair, 匙羹要用spoon，東京要用Tokyo<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然外界會覺得貽笑大方，不過在八婆世界之中的當局者，是逼於無奈，甚至是生死攸關"},{"pid":"74bc2a07c0f6a3a1a75b9a3fb331d87f478f15db","tid":2283003,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"This is the obscure war of our everyday interpersonal lives without physical violence... the bullets pierce through our soul and the blood is shed from our heart, but not our flesh.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9fUyul2Hg18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9fUyul2Hg18&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=92b46e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9fUyul2Hg18</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rG0Ws3YfONY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrG0Ws3YfONY&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6536ab47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rG0Ws3YfONY</a>"},{"pid":"f748880592fc034106e6cd7f64ae24ba04864628","tid":2283003,"uid":146369,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"即係SSGOCIPWTS？"},{"pid":"1ad91c6d0f2ac9bd362a146123a758d687032fdd","tid":2283003,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f748880592fc034106e6cd7f64ae24ba04864628","tid":2283003,"uid":146369,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"即係SSGOCIPWTS？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ac24d68ef2c8dbdb6f1bb259d7c1103f10404e","tid":2283003,"uid":132106,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"你自己開個google map黎睇啦~<br />\n你自己開個谷歌地圖黎睇啦~<br />\n有咩心理戰術係入面？<br />\n求分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0439032e775c841bb826178477a727073e871439","tid":2283003,"uid":47901,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"01ac24d68ef2c8dbdb6f1bb259d7c1103f10404e","tid":2283003,"uid":132106,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"你自己開個go